<a class="rounded-icon block-share__item block-share__item--pinterest js-blockshare-link" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20160303093826/http://www.pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?description=US+Navy+releases+footage+it+says+shows+Iranian+boats+firing+missiles+%E2%80%93+video&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2Fvideo%2F2016%2Fjan%2F13%2Fus-navy-releases-footage-it-says-shows-iranian-boats-firing-missiles-video&amp;media=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.guim.co.uk%2Fsys-images%2FGuardian%2FPix%2Faudio%2Fvideo%2F2016%2F1%2F12%2F1452642051276%2FKP_1337066_crop_640x360.jpg" target="_blank" data-link-name="social pinterest"> <span class="inline-share-pinterest inline-icon ">
